DIMENSION 1 — Speed & Mobile Experience
Does the site appear fast and mobile-ready, or is it likely slow and friction-heavy on phones?
Signals: PageSpeed score, website status, category size.

DIMENSION 2 — Patient Intake & Booking Funnel
How easy is it for a new patient to move from landing → understanding → contacting/booking?
Signals: booking_present, website_status, category type.

DIMENSION 3 — Tracking & Visibility
Does this practice likely track conversions, calls, and form submissions? Is their GBP claimed and active?
Signals: has_seo, gbp_unclaimed, social_count.

DIMENSION 4 — Compliance & Trust Patterns
Does the site show ADA-friendly patterns, privacy policy, HIPAA-aligned contact handling, and trust signals (reviews, credentials)?
Signals: website_status, has_seo, gbp_rating, gbp_review_count.

DIMENSION 5 — Patient Message Clarity
